        <briefdescription>
<para>Static constant indicating if From is convertible to To. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>If From is implicitly convertible to To:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Test(Create()) returns type To</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>sizeof(To) == sizeof(To) evaluates to true</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>If From is NOT implicitly convertible to To:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>The Test(From) overload causes substitution failure (SFINAE)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Test(AnyType) is selected instead, returning char</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>sizeof(char) == sizeof(To) evaluates to false (assuming To != char) </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
